column5: Want to try some downrigging at the beach for the first time. Where is the best place to launch. I have a 16 foot crestliner fish hawk, any help would be appriciated. Thanks Scooter
Hey Scooter, The Boat Launch is at Beach # 1
Thanks. Beach #1 is the park and is gated correct. Do you know what hours the park runs?
You can launch at Sturgeon Point marina. You have to pay anywhere you launch. We unloaded,no one there,paid when we got back in. Lot's of parking.
Thanks Davey buoy that sounds alot better. Scooter
